\pard\pardeftab640\slleading200\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 Substitutions
\f0\b0\fs24 \
Choose Edit > Substitutions to access text substitution features:\
\pard\pardeftab640\li360\fi-360\slleading200\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \'95 Smart Copy/Paste \'97 Automatically adjust spacing when cutting and pasting text.\
\'95 Smart Quotes \'97 Automatically convert straight quotes (" and ') to typographic (curly) quotes.\
